snippet.title: inFAMOUS: Power Trip Trailer
snippet.description:
This trailer showcases the player's ability to go anywhere and explore anything in the living world of inFAMOUS, Sucker Punch's open-world action adventure title exclusively for the PLAYSTATION®3 system. Check out the many different ways that inFAMOUS lets players use Cole's incredible powers to save what's left of Empire Cityor destroy it all!  The choice is up to you.  

Download the trailer today to see the possibilities!
